   * and either column B is not zero or column C is not zero.
  The formula will be:
  `=SUM(COUNTIFS('raw 1'!A2:A100000,$F4,'raw 1'!B2:B100000,"<>0"),COUNTIFS('raw 1'!A2:A100000,$F4,'raw 1'!C2:C100000,"<>0"))`
  (adjusted for each row by using $F4, $F5, …).
